* /c/tag: list of all the contents that match that tag;
* /d/filename: download the file from the download folder;
* /a/name: article;
* /b/name: breve;
* /m/filename: access a movie directly;
* /p/filename: access a picture directly;
* /s/name: static page;
* /w/name: access a presentation directly (but with the interface!);
* /t/name: access a presentation directly (but in presentation mode!);

* code a rss generation function;
